Dear Sir\Madam,


Please find the below ADS response for given points.



Service Account:-> You need to create application bind user id for that kindly raise the Score request with approved form. For Password reset you need to visit ADS Desk. Yes this user can read the users from child domain as well.


Port & Connectivity:-> You need to open port connectivity 3269,636 from your application server to our Root AD UAT server.

User Login Format:-> Your application bind user id will be created in Root UAT server and for authenticate users from MUM,AHM you may be login using below format. Eg: MUM\user id     To test the functionality and create the users in AHM and MUM domain, kindly raised the score request for id creation upto 5 users in UAT child domain. If your id is already present in AHM and MUM UAT domain then no need to create new id's.

Base DN Scope:-> Yes for Base DN you can used DC=UATAD,DC=SBI




Also additionally you need to import this UAT certificate in .cer format in your application.



For any other query or clarification kindly visit ADS desk.
